:'''Gilbert:''' (Trailblazer), young one, you arrive just in time! Come here, I have big news to share with you...
:'''Gilbert:''' Though I'm not sure it can be considered as good news... Youngsters from the Logistics Department were trying to convince me to stay after they heard that I was retiring... They said that they couldn't handle things correctly without me leading the way.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Maybe they were just being polite...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301111405-->
::'''Gilbert:''' You really think so? But they've even asked their superior about this...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Young people need to learn and grow by themselves.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301111407-->
::'''Gilbert:''' ...I thought the same at the beginning. But I wasn't expecting that they even asked their superior about this...
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_301111408-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301111408-->
:'''Gilbert:''' Then Dunn came to me and asked if I wanted to stay for another couple of months to train my successors.
:'''Gilbert:''' ...Ah, you know me, too shy to turn down such a sincere request!
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} So you've said yes?
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Then how about Lila?
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301111412-->
:'''Gilbert:''' I was a bit emotional at that point and agreed to his request.
:'''Gilbert:''' But when I gave it a second thought later, I felt bad for my wife and child... They have to wait for another handful of months.
:'''Gilbert:''' (Trailblazer), young one, are you willing to help me once again? I wrote a letter to my wife and child to explain my situation. If you could deliver my letter to Lila...
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Piece of cake.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301111416-->
::'''Gilbert:''' Many thanks! Hope those youngsters in the Logistics Department can be as reliable as you are.
:{{DIcon|Arrow}} Are you sure you won't regret it?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301111418-->
::'''Gilbert:''' Nothing to be regretful for... It would only be worth it to shine in my field for a while longer...
:<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_301111419-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301111419-->
