::'''Gilbert:''' I get it now &mdash; have you been playing with me? Do you think this is funny?
::'''Gilbert:''' *sigh* Young people nowadays really have no respect for the elders at all... But then again, without the ideas you mentioned, I'm afraid I won't be able to write this letter until next year.
::'''Gilbert:''' ...Anyway, thanks for stopping by. Here, for your trouble.
::'''Gilbert:''' Lila... Please don't be ashamed of Daddy! *sigh*
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
