::'''Gilbert:''' (Trailblazer)! I've been waiting for you, youngster. I was afraid that you might never come to the restricted zone...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_301110301_9-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_301110301_9-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Nice seeing you again, old man.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I have other things to do...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301110705-->
:::'''Gilbert:''' One minute, just one minute of your time! I'm begging you...
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_301110706-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301110706-->
::'''Gilbert:''' Uh, do you remember that letter I wanted to send to my wife and daughter? I finished writing it yesterday.
::'''Gilbert:''' If you don't mind, could you help take it to my daughter for me? It's an arduous process mailing things from inside the restricted zone. You need one approval after another... The letter would probably not even be sent before my service was up.
::'''Gilbert:''' Please, youngster! You're the only person I know who is able to freely move in and out of the restricted zone. If you don't help, then there is no hope for me to get this letter delivered!
::'''Gilbert:''' My daughter's name is Lila. She and her mother live in the Administrative District. Thanks for doing this, youngster...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
