::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301111102-->
::'''Gilbert:''' (Trailblazer), you're back so soon! Young people these days really are quick on their feet.
::'''Gilbert:''' Did you go see Lila? And did you give her my letter? What did she say?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_301110305_10-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_301110305_10-->
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} She wrote a letter for you in reply.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Relax, here, take a look...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_301111106-->
::'''Gilbert:''' Sh&mdash;She wrote back to me? Quick, let me read it...
::'''Gilbert:''' ...
::'''Gilbert:''' Lila...
::'''Gilbert:''' I've been so stubborn... avoiding my own family, making up such ridiculous lies...
::'''Gilbert:''' I get it now... Even if I don't have any great achievements over these past twenty-plus years, my family will always be by my side. What I was worrying over... Tsk, it's funny to think about now, haha.
::'''Gilbert:''' Thank you for all your help, stranger! Please take these... Now I need to go get my things together and get ready to return home.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
