:{{DIcon}} How have things been?
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 501029605: Config/Level/Mission/5010296/Act/Act501029605.json-->
::'''Gilbert:''' I've still waiting to hear back about my leave application. I heard there are a lotta people ahead of me in the line...
::'''Gilbert:''' But pressure on the front line has receded a lot these days, so everyone just wants to take a break and reunite with their families. I just have no idea how long it's gonna take until my turn...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What's changed on the front line?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029649-->
:::'''Gilbert:''' Well, I heard the monsters on the front line have dwindled recently... But that's just some people talking. I'm just a logistics guy, I've never set foot on the battleground before.
:::'''Gilbert:''' But the vibe here has really changed. Back when things were more serious, this restricted zone used to seem so solemn. But now, just look &mdash; everyone's spirits are completely different...
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} That's good then. I wish you a speedy return to your homelands.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Hope you can get home soon.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029653-->
::'''Gilbert:''' Haha, here's hoping! Once I get home, I'll have to catch up on spending time with the family...
